SEASON 7 ( 2018 ) HOME MEDIA Section::::Home media .
A DVD collection of all the episodes from seasons 1–4 , titled Spirit Riding Free : Season 1–4 was released on DVD on June 5 , 2018 by Universal Pictures Home Entertainment .
The series is also scheduled for DVD releases in the UK , France , Italy , and Germany .
